---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
---
<div class="guide-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<SectionWrapper bg="base" id="about" overflow="visible" class="guide-section">
  <!-- Section label -->
  <p class="section-label">// 03 ABOUT</p>

  <!-- Two-column layout -->
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <!-- LEFT column: empathy copy -->
    <div class="empathy-col">
      <p class="empathy-opener">
        You've already tried the obvious answers.
      </p>

      <div class="empathy-body">
        <p>
          The template site from the platform everyone recommended. The freelancer
          who promised a two-week redesign. The agency that showed you a beautiful
          deck and disappeared after launch. The app that was going to sync
          everything. The AI tool you signed up for, used twice, and now pay for
          every month anyway.
        </p>

        <p>
          None of it worked because none of it started with a diagnosis. Someone
          sold you a solution before asking what was actually broken.
        </p>

        <p>
          Every project starts the same way. Map the systems. Find what's broken.
          Write a problem statement you can read and agree on before a line of
          code gets touched. One person runs the entire build — no handoffs, no
          account managers between you and the work. That's Maximum Execution,
          based in Richmond, Virginia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT column: testimonials -->
    <div class="proof-col">
      <div class="testimonials">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-header">
            <cite class="log-meta">Marcus T. // Commercial Cleaning Co. // Richmond, VA</cite>
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-body">
            "I'd paid two different agencies to rebuild our site over three years. Both times I ended up with something that looked fine but still didn't bring in clients. Spencer ran the diagnostic first, and it identified exactly why. Our message was buried and there was no follow-up system. Six weeks later we had a site that generated 11 qualified leads in the first month. That had never happened before."
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-header">
            <cite class="log-meta">Priya S. // HR Consulting Practice // Charlotte, NC</cite>
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-body">
            "I expected this to take two or three months. My site was live in eight days. More importantly, I actually understood what was built and why. I got documentation I could read, not a codebase I'd never open. We booked three new clients in the first two weeks from form submissions alone. I didn't even know the form was being used."
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-header">
            <cite class="log-meta">Daniel W. // Residential Property Mgmt // Raleigh, NC</cite>
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-body">
            "I came to the diagnostic not knowing if I needed a new website, better software, or something else entirely. The questions forced me to think about my business differently. By the end I had a clearer picture of where I was losing people than I'd had in two years of running it. We ended up building a client intake app that replaced four separate tools. My team hasn't complained about our software once since it launched."
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section bottom rule -->
  <div class="section-bottom-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Amber divider rule at top */
  .guide-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.15);
  }

  /* Section label - monospace, small, amber at 35% */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Two-column grid */
  .guide-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 4fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ── Empathy column ── */
  .empathy-opener {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .empathy-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .empathy-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── Proof column ── */
  .proof-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  /* ── Testimonials ── */
  .testimonials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .testimonial {
    background: oklch(0.12 0.02 85);
    border: 1px solid oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .testimonial-header {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .log-meta {
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .testimonial-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
  }

  /* ── Section bottom rule ── */
  .section-bottom-rule {
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.20);
    margin-top: var(--space-20);
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  /* ── Desktop sticky scroll ── */
  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .empathy-col {
      position: sticky;
      top: 80px;
      height: calc(100vh - 160px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-self: start;
    }
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .guide-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }

    /* Reorder: proof column first, empathy last */
    .proof-col {
      order: -1;
    }

    .empathy-col {
      order: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
